high_descs: Go forward to the dining table, then hang a left and go to the table with the plant on it.
Pick up the pencil that is on the table.
Turn to the right and go to the dining table.
Put the pencil on the gray plate that is on the dining table.
Pick up the gray plate that is on the dining table.
Turn left, go forward past the couch, then turn left and go to the table that is in front of the couch.
Put the plate on the table to the right of the white vase.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate and pencil on a table.

high_descs: Move to the end table to the right of the fire place
Pick up a pencil from the end table
Move to the dining table to the right of you
Put the pencil on a plate on the table
Pick up a plate from the table with the pencil
Move to the coffee table to the left of the fire place
Place the plate on the coffee table
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with a pen on the coffee table.

high_descs: Go forward, turn left at the table, move forward, then turn right to face the table with a plant on it.
Pick up the pencil on the table, to the left of the keys.
Turn right, move forward, then turn left to face the table.
Put the pencil on the plate, on the table.
Pick up the plate from the table.
Turn left, go forward, turn left, then go forward to face the table in front of the couch.
Put the plate on the table, to the right of the vase.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with a pencil on it on the table.
